T04TD3942E:195b-1: shiksha sa mu tstsha ya aa bhi sa ma ya n'a ma /
T04TD3942E:195b-3: bslab pa kun las btus pa'i mngon par rtogs pa zhes bya ba /
T04TD3942E:195b-4: bcom ldan 'das 'jam pa'i rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T04TD3942E:195b-5: stobs bcu ldan pa gang gi zhabs rdul la //
T04TD3942E:195b-6: lha rnams cod pan gyis gtugs de btud de //
T04TD3942E:195b-7: 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyi zhabs gtugs zhi ba'i lhas //
T04TD3942E:195b-8: bslab pa'i gnas rnams mdo sde kun las btus //
T04TD3942E:195b-9: dang po gnyis ni phyi ma bdun gyis bshad //
T04TD3942E:195b-10: gnyis kyi don ni rnam dgur shes par bya //
T04TD3942E:195b-11: lnga yi 'og dang gnyis kyi gong ma ni //
T04TD3942E:195b-12: dang po yin te gzhan na gnyis pa yin //
T04TD3942E:195b-13: gnyis ka'i don ni zla ba tshes pa dang //
T04TD3942E:195b-14: nya dang sdig pa gser gyi 'khor lo dang //
T04TD3942E:195b-15: glang po gdugs dang thig le dang po dang //
T04TD3942E:195b-16: 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyi phyag na ral gri 'dzin //
T04TD3942E:195b-17: rin po che ni khyad par gnyis dang bcas //
T04TD3942E:195b-18: dad dang bla ma'i tshogs dang go cha dang //
T04TD3942E:195b-19: byin rlabs phyir mi ldog dang spyod pa dang //
T04TD3942E:195b-20: lung bstan pa sku gsum yon tan bcas //
T04TD3942E:195b-21: bzhi las 'bras bur gyur pa dang po ste //
T04TD3942E:195b-22: gsum ni yang dag spong bar rab tu gnas //
T04TD3942E:195b-23: gnyen po gang la de yi ngo bo ste //
T04TD3942E:195b-24: rten dang nyes pa spong ba dang po yin //
T04TD3942E:195b-25: sun 'byin pa ni de yi gnyis par brjod //
T04TD3942E:195b-26: gnyen po spyod pa gnyis pa'i dang po ste //
T04TD3942E:195b-27: spyod pa tha ma de yi gnyis pa yin //
T04TD3942E:195b-28: mi mthun pa ni rnam pa brgyad yin te //
T04TD3942E:195b-29: las dang nyon mongs lta ba dag las ni //
T04TD3942E:195b-30: 'gyur dang gyur pa'i khyad par rnam pa drug / rang gi rtsa ba tha ma gnyis dang bcas //
T04TD3942E:195b-31: 'gyur ba gsum ni dang po'i chos su gzhag / gyur pa gsum ni dang po'i gnyis pa ste //
T04TD3942E:196a-1: gnyis kyang de dang mthun pa yin //
T04TD3942E:196a-2: gyur pa gsum ni gnyis pa'i gnyis pa ste //
T04TD3942E:196a-3: rten gyi dang po'i chos kyang de yi yin //
T04TD3942E:196a-4: gyur pa dang po stobs kyi dang po ste //
T04TD3942E:196a-5: gyur pa gnyis pa phung po'i gnyis pa yin //
T04TD3942E:196a-6: gyur pa gsum pa phung po'i gsum pa ste//
T04TD3942E:196a-7: mi mthun gnyen po'i khyad par de yis bstan //
T04TD3942E:196a-8: tshogs kyi lam la lnga ni dngos yin te //
T04TD3942E:196a-9: de las gzhan pa rjes su mthun pa yin //
T04TD3942E:196a-10: sbyor ba'i lam la bdun ni dngos yin te //
T04TD3942E:196a-11: de las gzhan pa lnga ni rjes mthun yin //
T04TD3942E:196a-12: mthong ba'i lam la bcu ni dngos yin te //
T04TD3942E:196a-13: de las gzhan pa gnyis ni rjes mthun yin //
T04TD3942E:196a-14: tshogs kyi lam la bsrung ba gtso bo ste //
T04TD3942E:196a-15: chos gzhan gsum po mos pa mchog dang ldan //
T04TD3942E:196a-16: sbyor ba'i lam la spel ba gtso bo ste //
T04TD3942E:196a-17: gsum po dag la ji ltar 'tsham par zad //
T04TD3942E:196a-18: mthong ba'i lam la dag pa gtso bo ste //
T04TD3942E:196a-19: gsum po dag gis bdag dang gzhan gyi don //
T04TD3942E:196a-20: bsgom pa'i lam la pha rol phyin pa ste //
T04TD3942E:196a-21: bsdu ba'i dngos po 'gro ba tshim par byed //
T04TD3942E:196a-22: bslab pa kun las btus pa'i mngon par rtogs pa zhes bya ba rdzogs so /
T04TD3942E:196a-24: // / dpal mar me mdzad ye shes dang /
T04TD3942E:196a-25: dge slong tshul khrims rgyal bas bsgyur ba'o //
T04TD3942E:196a-26: gser gling rgyal po dpal ldan chos skyong gis //
T04TD3942E:196a-27: bcom ldan 'jam pa'i rdo rje mnyes byas pas //
T04TD3942E:196a-28: bslab pa kun las btus pa'i mngon par rtogs //
T04TD3942E:196a-29: ka ma la dang mar me mdzad la gsungs /
